$\frac{5}{3}\times\frac{6}{10}\times\frac{15}{9}\times\frac{12}{20}\times\frac{25}{15}\times\frac{18}{30}\times\frac{35}{21}\times\frac{24}{40}$
$= \frac{5}{3}\times\frac{6}{10}\times\frac{15}{9}\times\frac{12}{20}\times\frac{25}{15}\times\frac{18}{30}\times\frac{35}{21}\times\frac{24}{40}$
$= \frac{5\times6\times15\times12\times25\times18\times35\times24}{3\times10\times9\times20\times15\times30\times21\times40}$
$= \frac{5\times(3\times2)\times(3\times5)\times(3\times2^2)\times(5^2)\times(2\times3^2)\times(5\times7)\times(2^3\times3)}{3\times(2\times5)\times(3^2)\times(2^2\times5)\times(3\times5)\times(2\times3\times5)\times(3\times7)\times(2^3\times5)}$
$= \frac{(5\times3\times2\times3\times5\times3\times2^2\times5^2\times2\times3^2\times5\times7\times2^3\times3)}{(3\times2\times5\times3^2\times2^2\times5\times3\times5\times2\times3\times7\times2^3\times5)}$
$= \frac{(5^1\times3^1\times2^1\times3^1\times5^1\times3^1\times2^2\times5^2\times2^1\times3^2\times5^1\times7\times2^3\times3)}{(3^1\times2^1\times5^1\times3^2\times2^2\times5^1\times3^1\times5^1\times2^1\times3^1\times7\times2^3\times5)}$
$= \frac{2^{1+2+3}\times3^{1+1+1+2}\times5^{1+1+2+1+1}\times7^{1}}{2^{1+2+1+3}\times3^{2+1+1+1}\times5^{1+1+1+1}\times7^{1}}$
$= \frac{2^6 \times 3^5 \times 5^5 \times 7^1}{2^7 \times 3^5 \times 5^4 \times 7^1}$
$= \frac{2^6 \times 3^5 \times 5^5}{2^7 \times 3^5 \times 5^4} \times 1$
$= \frac{1}{2} \times \frac{5^5}{5^4}$
$= \frac{1}{2} \times 5^1 = \frac{5}{2}$
Final Answer: $\boxed{2.5}$
